# Canonical line endings for modfolio-universe.
#
# All tracked files default to LF. Windows checkouts see LF too — we do NOT
# let git auto-convert to CRLF on checkout, because biome + bun tooling and
# the harness-pull manifest comparison both expect LF consistently. Reported
# by gistcore (Issue 5) + modfolio-pay (IMPROVEMENT-5, 2026-04-16): CRLF
# drift produced spurious "merged: 3" entries in every pull-manifest.
#
# Binary file types must be listed explicitly so git does not attempt to
# touch them as text.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
